OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChina seeks to lift        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhomework pressures on      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fschoolchildren             
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, China has passed an education law aimed
OL,6, at reducing the pressures of excessive 
OL,7, homework and intensive after-school    
OL,8, tutoring, state media say.             
OL,10,FParents are being asked to ensure their
OL,11,Fchildren have reasonable time for rest 
OL,12,Fand exercise, and do not spend too much
OL,13,Ftime online.                           
OL,15,FIn August China banned written exams   
OL,16,Ffor six and seven year olds.           
OL,18,FOfficials warned at the time that      
OL,19,Fstudents' physical and mental health   
OL,20,Fwas being harmed.                      
